        {
            "title": "歐盟達成協議將加強對外商投資審查力度 旨在保護本地區經濟",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 歐盟就加強對外商直接投資審查達成初步協議，此舉旨在幫助保護當地經濟免受中美兩國政策影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">周四達成的協議將賦予歐盟更多權力，可對影響公共秩序和安全的外國投資進行審查和干預。該協議還將為審查此類投資設定歐盟基本標準，目前尚無此類標準。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們達成了一個平衡且相稱的框架，重點關注最敏感的技術和基礎設施，」丹麥工業、商業和金融事務部長Morten Bodskov表示。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐盟理事會與歐洲議會談判代表於周四上午敲定協議。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4570e7b9-108a-3aae-abde-1bcba1ef59dd-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在歐洲應對川普關稅戰及中國對關鍵原物料實施限制之際，歐盟通過制定更嚴格的指導方針來保護本地區經濟。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本月早些時候，歐盟發布了經濟安全綱領，強調必須確保外來投資不會使關鍵領域暴露於敵對所有權之下。綱領同時堅持要求，此類投資應為歐盟創造附加值，而非削弱歐盟的技術優勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：歐盟披露新的經濟安全計畫 專注六大高風險領域以保持產業優勢</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題EU Reaches Deal to Heighten Foreign Investment Screening</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E9%81%94%E6%88%90%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%E5%B0%87%E5%8A%A0%E5%BC%B7%E5%B0%8D%E5%A4%96%E5%95%86%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%AF%A9%E6%9F%A5%E5%8A%9B%E5%BA%A6-%E6%97%A8%E5%9C%A8%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%8D%80%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F-114218861.html",
