        {
            "title": "中國外交部長王毅將訪問阿聯酋、沙烏地、約旦 以拓展各領域交流合作",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國外交部長王毅將於近日訪問中東地區，包括沙烏地阿拉伯等國。中東對於<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:世界第二大經濟體;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/世界第二大經濟體\">世界第二大經濟體</a>中國的能源需求而言至關重要。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國外交部周四表示，王毅將於12月12日至16日訪問阿聯酋、沙烏地、約旦。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">外交部發言人郭嘉昆在例行記者會上表示，中國將藉此機會同三國「拓展各領域交流合作」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國約三分之二的原油進口自中東，也是沙烏地阿拉伯最大的原油買家之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近年來，北京試圖在該地區發揮更大作用，成效不一。雖然中國在2023年促成伊朗與沙烏地實現外交緩和，但今年衝突導致該地區局勢不穩之際，中國未過於積極地介入。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2e8af5ce-d822-356c-8657-105d0522e3d3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China’s Top Diplomat to Visit Saudi Arabia on Middle East Trip</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Yongchang Chin.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%96%E4%BA%A4%E9%83%A8%E9%95%B7%E7%8E%8B%E6%AF%85%E5%B0%87%E8%A8%AA%E5%95%8F%E9%98%BF%E8%81%AF%E9%85%8B-%E6%B2%99%E7%83%8F%E5%9C%B0-%E7%B4%84%E6%97%A6-%E4%BB%A5%E6%8B%93%E5%B1%95%E5%90%84%E9%A0%98%E5%9F%9F%E4%BA%A4%E6%B5%81%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C-113606046.html",
